comments.body:
@nalind how will this be used?  Do you already have any use case in mind?

I am playing with something similar in container-libs/storage to allow copying a layer while preserving reflinks (https://github.com/containers/container-libs/pull/651) and @cgwalters suggested json-rpc for that.

Would it make sense to unify on the protocol (and dependencies)?  @cgwalters would grpc work for composefs?
